{"/service/ndnp/gu/batch_gu_alicorn_ver02/data/sn89077295/00517010674/1948111801/0150.xml":{"full_text":"Thursday, November 18.1918\nHow Do You Look\nBy Bessie F. Bell\nEvery woman who makes an\nhonest attempt to keep herself look\ning as attractive as she can, will\nenjoy reading the following list\ncf 10 musts for beruty. As a\nbeauty stylist believes:\nGet busy and restore yourself\nto normal weight. Whether you\nare under or over weight. You\nknow, according to the weight\nscale the healthy woman of 50\nshould weight no more than she\ndid at 25.\nwalking ersdv and\ngracefully. Sit and stand naturally\nand realxed.\nIk w while resting\nor sleeping so that your mind as\nwell as your body is in repose.\nLearning to relaxe is a mental\nachievement.\nFind Ge me t effective and be\ncoming way of fixing your face\na-d your hair and do both each\ntime you dress or make-up.\nSpend^JO minutes daily or\nsimple skin care and you will\nalways have a lovely skin. Where\nprecious beauty is in the balance\none ounce of prevention is wort!\n10 pounds of cure. Never, never\ngo to bed with your make-up on.\nNow, here is that word again\u2014\nyour daily dozens. If you do them\nfaithfully and properly, girls,\nhere is what you will -get\u2014 a\nstraight spine, a raised bust, a\nflat abdomen, squared shoulders,\na beautiful neckline and a slender\nproportioned figure that has beer\nFOR QUALITY ALWAYS\nJOHN G. Butler Company\nEverything Your House Needs\nB. P. S. Paints Building Fdaterials Mill work\nHardware Glass\nStore: 2-1161 Plant 2-1164\n91 Years of Service\nCongress and Whitaker Sts. 54th and Montgomery Sts-\nh\u25a0 7\nI Wb aWMI\n,HC\nn d molded into bet\nter contours.\nMake a daily habit of being\nfemmine. Woman is symbolic of\ncleanliness and daintiness.\nCultivate a soft pleasing voice\nand attractive gestures. Be polite\nand courteous whether at home\nor work.\nIt has been said that women\neither have that magnetic some\nth;ny tha L draws people to them\nor they have not